# Branch pipeline

```text
dev → PR → preview   (preview EAS builds, internal)
preview → PR → main  (CI only)
main → PR → production (production build + auto-submit to Play internal + TestFlight)
```

- Do not push directly to `main` or `production` without PR
- Production submit credentials live on EAS, not local paths in `eas.json`
- Docs: `docs/github-actions-preview.md`, `docs/github-actions-production.md`
